abstract: Soccer Roundup; England defeats Germany, 1-0, at Women's World Cup soccer tournament; other soccer news noted.
lead_paragraph: It was England’s first win in 21 meetings against Germany, and it also secured the team’s best finish in its four Women’s World Cup appearances.

headline.main: England Tops Germany for Third Place at World Cup
headline.print_headline: Consolation for England at World Cup
